'''Hawsa''' ({{IPAc-en|ˈ|h|aʊ|s|ə}}) (Yaren Hawsa ama Harshen Hawsa) waa afka Chadic (laan ka mid ah qoyska afka Afro-Luqatul) oo leh tirada ugu badan ee ku hadla, hadlay sida luqaddooda kowaad ay ku saabsan 34 milyan oo qof, iyo sidii luqad labaad by qiyaastii 18 milyan oo dheeraad ah, total qiyaastii waa 52 milyan oo qof.<ref>''Ethnologue'' (2009) cites 18,5 million L1 and 15 million L2 speakers in Nigeria in 1991; 5.5 million L1 speakers and half that many L2 speakers in Niger in 2006, 0.8 million in Benin in 2006, and just over 1 million in other countries.</ref>

